FAT FREEZING CRYO LIPO 4 cups 50% OFF

non-surgical permanent fat removal

 

Fat freezing is a non-invasive alternative to liposuction. Through the controlled application of cooling cups with temperature ranging from +5 to -11 °C, the procedure reduces fat cell volume by up to 30%.

By the end of the freezing treatment, the targeted fat cells gradually die off and are expelled through the body’s natural elimination process. For this reason, the end result can be seen up to three months later. Fat Freezing sessions can be done only once per month. This treatment is recommended in conjunction with Pressotherapy. 

BENEFITS:

  • Reduction of fat tissue
  • Body shaping and contouring
  • Skin tightening and toning
  • Cellulite reduction

BOTOX

10%OF

LOOK YOUNGER FOR LONGER

Botox is one of our most popular treatments at Body Lab Bali. Botox blocks nerve activity in the muscles, causing a temporary reduction in muscle activity, which in turn reduces wrinkles and sagging.

We use only the highest quality Allergan Botox from USA and all injectables are administered by an experienced medical professional.

Effects last about three to eight months, depending on what concern you are addressing.

Where can we use the Botox to look younger?

  • Forehead between the eyes, frown lines.
  • Eyebrows (to combat droopiness)
  • Crows feet 
  • Smokers line on the upper lip 
  • Age lines on the neck 

Botox can also be used to treat excessive underarm sweating.

Skin Boosters are micro-injections of very smooth dermal filler that contains hyaluronic acid. 3-in-1 super facial

Oxygeneo is a 3-in-1 super facial that exfoliates, nourishes and delivers skin oxygenation. Similar to microdermabrasion, the Oxygeneo exfoliates the upper skin layer to remove dead cells, preparing it to absorb nutrient-rich active ingredients.

CO2 bubbles are then applied to the skin, creating a physiological response, that sends oxygen-rich blood to the area, increasing capillary flow and skin metabolism. Expect to see younger looking skin after your very first treatment.

MICRODERMABRASION

10%OFF  

Microdermabrasion is a non-invasive procedure that uses tiny crystals to help remove the superficial layer of dead skin cells. When the stratum corneum (outermost layer of the epidermis) or the top layer of skin, the body interprets it as an injury. It then quickly replaces the lost skin cells with new, healthy ones. 

The procedure uses a special applicator with an abrasive surface to gently sand away the thick outer layer of the skin to rejuvenate it and this is safe for any skin color. 

The goal of microdermabrasion is to make a person's complexion smoother, brighter, and make the skin appear more even.

Benefit: 

  • Dullness in the complexion

  • Uneven skin tone

  • Uneven skin texture

  • Age spots

  • Dark spots that can form after acne clears up

  • Melasma, a common issue that forms dark spots or patches on the skin

PRP Platelet-rich plasma

VAMPIRE FACIAL & HAIR GROWTH

 15% OFF

The Platelet-Rich Plasma (PRP facial), also known as the vampire facial, includes drawing blood from your arm, separating the platelets, and then injecting them into your skin via microneedling injections. The doctor runs the needle pen over your face while squirting the platelets into the mini injection holes. Since the platelets are high in growth hormone, and the microneedling stimulates the skin to regenerate, the entire procedure is meant to aid cell turnover and give you a radiant, youthful visage.

Benefits of PRP Facial Rejuvenation:

  • Increases collagen production
  • Reduction of fine lines and wrinkles
  • Firmer, tighter skin
  • Improves moisture retention
  • Enhances skin tone and texture
  • Reduces hyperpigmentation and pore size
  • Minimizes broken capillaries and spider veins
  • Improves skin texture and appearance of scars

PRP (platelet-rich plasma) therapy for hair loss is a three-step medical treatment in which a person’s blood is drawn, processed, and then injected into their scalp⁠.

PRP injections trigger natural hair growth and maintain its strength by increasing  both the blood supply to the hair follicle and the thickness of the hair shaft.⁠

⁠For more severe cases, this effective approach can be combined with other hair loss procedures or medications. 

⁠PRP is the BEST solution for hair loss and to boost healthy & strong hair growth .

⁠Benefits:

  • Prevention of hair loss
  • Enhancement of new hair growth
  • Stronger and shinier hair
